{"type":"message","id":"fc84ade4","parentId":"909bb1de","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:32:49.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gmail script is failing with an authentication error. The calendar script is missing. These are likely the culprits causing the timeout - the skill is trying to run scripts that don't work or hang.\n\nLet me fix both:\n1. The calendar script is referenced in SKILL.md but doesn't exist in the directory\n2. The Gmail script has auth issues\n\nLet me look at the SKILL.md to see how these are called, and then figure out the right fixes.","thinkingSignature":"02ee9dfbc96e7974b965600baf5156e018b2cdf16646f542fabb389a926cd2e3"},{"type":"text","text":"Found the problem. Two issues:\n\n1. **Calendar script missing** — `get_calendar.scpt` doesn't exist in the skill folder\n2. **Gmail auth is broken** — credentials need refresh\n\nBoth cause the skill to hang until timeout. Let me fix the Gmail auth first:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o87jil4mfeij_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/skills/morning-brief/gmail_script.py 2>/dev/null | head -40"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25145,"output":201,"cacheRead":26978,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775471563099,"responseId":"0622becbf001926e94390b69c5510c5f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad82cac6","parentId":"fc84ade4","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:32:49.348Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o87jil4mfeij_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import json\nfrom google.oauth2.credentials import Credentials\nfrom google.auth.transport.requests import Request\nfrom googleapiclient.discovery import build\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nwith open('/Users/bobbygalletta/.config/gmail_oauth/credentials.json') as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\n    \ncreds = Credentials(\n    token=data['token'],\n    refresh_token=data['refresh_token'],\n    client_id=data['client_id'],\n    client_secret=data['client_secret'],\n    token_uri=data['token_uri'],\n)\n\nif creds.expired:\n    creds.refresh(Request())\n\nservice = build('gmail', 'v1', credentials=creds)\n\n# Get emails from yesterday AND today\nyesterday = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=1)).strftime(\"%Y/%m/%d\")\nquery = f'in:inbox after:{yesterday}'\n\nres = service.users().messages().list(userId='me', q=query, maxResults=100).execute()\nmsgs = res.get('messages', [])\nprint(f'Total: {len(msgs)}')\n\nfor m in msgs:\n    msg = service.users().messages().get(userId='me', id=m['id'], format='full').execute()\n    headers = {h['name']: h['value'] for h in msg['payload'].get('headers', [])}\n    sender = headers.get('From', '')\n    subject = headers.get('Subject', '')\n    date_h = headers.get('Date', '')\n    labels = msg.get('labelIds', [])\n    is_unread = 'UNREAD' in labels\n    print(f'[{\"UNREAD\" if is_unread else \"READ\"}] {sender[:30]} | {subject[:60]}')"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8,"aggregated":"import json\nfrom google.oauth2.credentials import Credentials\nfrom google.auth.transport.requests import Request\nfrom googleapiclient.discovery import build\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nwith open('/Users/bobbygalletta/.config/gmail_oauth/credentials.json') as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\n    \ncreds = Credentials(\n    token=data['token'],\n    refresh_token=data['refresh_token'],\n    client_id=data['client_id'],\n    client_secret=data['client_secret'],\n    token_uri=data['token_uri'],\n)\n\nif creds.expired:\n    creds.refresh(Request())\n\nservice = build('gmail', 'v1', credentials=creds)\n\n# Get emails from yesterday AND today\nyesterday = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=1)).strftime(\"%Y/%m/%d\")\nquery = f'in:inbox after:{yesterday}'\n\nres = service.users().messages().list(userId='me', q=query, maxResults=100).execute()\nmsgs = res.get('messages', [])\nprint(f'Total: {len(msgs)}')\n\nfor m in msgs:\n    msg = service.users().messages().get(userId='me', id=m['id'], format='full').execute()\n    headers = {h['name']: h['value'] for h in msg['payload'].get('headers', [])}\n    sender = headers.get('From', '')\n    subject = headers.get('Subject', '')\n    date_h = headers.get('Date', '')\n    labels = msg.get('labelIds', [])\n    is_unread = 'UNREAD' in labels\n    print(f'[{\"UNREAD\" if is_unread else \"READ\"}] {sender[:30]} | {subject[:60]}')","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775471569299}}
