.me/Unsubscribed,CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS\\\" --add INBOX\\n\\nSTEP 4: For any genuinely new emails:\\n- Read the email: gog gmail get <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n- Apply labels per Bobby's Email Assistant Skill rules in /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/SecondBrain/Email/EMAIL_ASSISTANT_SKILL.md\\n- Apply Gmail labels: gog gmail labels add <msg_id> '<LabelName>' --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n\\nSTEP 5: Send Telegram summary to 8212808444:\\n```\\n📬 NEW MAIL (X new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Snippet]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Snippet]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Snippet]\\n```\\n\\nSTEP 6: Update timestamp: echo $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\\n\\nSTEP 7: If no new emails, send a simple confirmation: \\\"✅ Email check done — no new emails\\\" to confirm the cron ran.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n        \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n        \"bestEffort\": false\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775474000767,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775470400767,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 13220,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      },\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"487e71b7-8898-4da8-8e53-5237c045750c\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Flonase Morning Reminder\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775441057467,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775441057467,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 9 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Ameri