{"type":"message","id":"0e51d643","parentId":"2c0dd692","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:33:14.907Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📖 BIBLE VERSE OF THE DAY\n\n\"Therefore confess your sins to each other and pray for each other so that you may be healed. The prayer of a righteous man is powerful and effective.\"\n— James 5:16 (NIV)\n\n💡 TODAY'S MOTIVATION: Fresh start Monday. You've got bills coming up (KUB due today, T-Mobile on the 10th), your job search pushing forward with new Indeed and ZipRecruiter emails, and a package waiting at Amazon Locker. Lean on the people around you — confide in Logan, delegate to your team, and don't carry everything alone. When you share the load, things get lighter. Today's verse is about honest community and mutual support. Use it."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775478794900}}
