condBrain/Finances/April_Bills.md\\\"\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775495580598,\n      \"responseId\": \"06231c9c76be2f70c42187eca6e6afc9\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"706c8bd3\",\n        \"seq\": 621\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Message sent to Dean. The dollar amounts got truncated in the transfer (a known issue with the agent-message script) but the full file path is there so Dean can read it himself.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Done! Sent to Dean. The dollar amounts got a little garbled in the transfer but the file path is there so he can pull it directly. \\n\\nHe should have it! 🧊💸\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775495585649,\n      \"responseId\": \"06231ca1f8b0532d367c898c2414efc1\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"8eec0a54\",\n        \"seq\": 623\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Hey Finn - Bobby says you have April bills ready. Can you tell me the file path and give me a summary of what's due in April?\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1775495700952,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"webchat\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      },\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"88e5658b\",\n        \"seq\": 624\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assis